          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一频一笑总关情，暗自伤心曲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家貂蝉。想爹爹将我送与太师成妾，连日伏待，今日无一事，不免到凤仪亭，"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "耍息一回，以消闷怀。来此已是凤仪亭，不免口占一词。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒醉凤仪亭，凤凰不见来。乌鸦入凤群，独自闷忧怀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那边好似温侯。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吕布上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我且躲在一旁，听她说些什么。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吕布听。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "貂蝉 （锁南枝） 妾命薄，泪暗流，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无媒径路羞错走。勉强侍衾绸。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我欲见温侯。啊呀，温侯吓，怎能勾？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吕布 （锁南枝） 青青柳，姣又柔，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一枝已折在他人手。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "良缘叹非偶。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这玉连环空在手。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，温侯吓，你好负心也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎说我负心？"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想我爹爹送奴与温侯成亲，不知你往哪里去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虎牢关上收兵去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "及见狂且。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了，哪个是狂且？"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是太师！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他便怎样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他便顿起不良之心，把我邀入府中淫污，我恨不得一死。今日得见温侯，哎呀，"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "死亦瞑目也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依小姐待要如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但凭温侯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，只恨我虎牢关上来迟了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（红衲袄） 只指望上秦楼吹凤箫，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又谁知抱琵琶弹别调。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带宽了舞东风杨柳腰。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "羞见你转秋波颜色姣。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何不当初不见高。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "温侯吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（红衲袄） 你只图虎牢关上功绩高，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "顿忘了凤头簪恩爱好。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "同心带，急嚷嚷被他扯断了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "玉连环，矻碀碀想你捶碎了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愿死在池中恨始消。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今生不得与你为夫妻，非盖世英雄也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "貂蝉 （红衲袄） 若念夫妻情义，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也把我尸骇覆草茅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "温侯请上，受奴一拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小将也有一拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "貂蝉。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（董卓上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，你不是吕布么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是吕布。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（貂蝉下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "反了反了。你不在虎牢关上干正事，来在凤仪亭中戏我的爱姬。戏我的爱姬是"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何道理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那王司徒将貂蝉许配于我，是你谋占！"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了，哪个谋占？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是你谋占！"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放屁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前番待你多亲近，把我爱姬来调引。巧弄拙，做出这般行径！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么叫“行径”？"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你把我当什么人看待？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不过是义父罢了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "却又来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既称父子昧彝伦，顿叫人心中发恨。真发恨，把那方天画戟留下了残生！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今天怒尤恨，怒尤恨。既称父子美议论，美议论。何必起这心中留占！"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪个留占？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是你留占。"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。是我留占。哈哈，你来你来吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休得要笑中藏刃。笑中藏刃，顿起人心中发硬。不念父子恩深，把方天画戟了"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "残生，了残生！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吕布下，李儒上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李儒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要动手，不要动手！"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好奴才，好奴才！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李儒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是李、是李儒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还是吕布？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李儒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是李儒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李儒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。太师为何这等着恼？"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "反了反了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李儒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "点兵剿捕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，不是吓。那吕布反了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李儒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？怎么反了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他不在虎牢关上干正事，来在凤仪亭中戏我的爱姬，戏我的爱姬！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李儒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，太师，可记得楚庄王的故事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，这奴才，忙碌碌讲起故事来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李儒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吕布既爱貂蝉，太师何不赐之？"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴才怎讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李儒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何不赐之？"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放屁，我的爱姬赐与吕布，你的妻子可能让于他？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李儒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的不能。"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你的不能，我的倒能？快快传李肃前来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李儒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请李肃将军。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李肃上。李儒下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李肃",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忽听太师唤，慌忙到跟前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见太师。"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狗才狗才！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（董卓打李肃。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何打起小人来了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你举荐的好人吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我荐的哪个？"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那吕布不是你荐的么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "荐的不差。"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他不在虎牢关前镇守，来在府中凤仪亭上戏我的爱姬。戏我的爱姬是何道理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太师，吕布既爱貂蝉，何不赐之？"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你家的妻子肯让与人罢！过来，你去到那王司徒家中，问他貂蝉送与吕布，就"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不该送与太师；既送与太师，就不该送与吕布。吓，一个人送将来不明不白，"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "弄得我父子，终朝每日，吃醋咽酸，是何道理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "分得明白便罢，分不明白，将首级回府！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李肃下。貂蝉上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀……"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掩面悲啼，自恨泪珠弹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看你泪珠垂，似梨花一枝。卿为何低了头，倒到在人怀里，全不念礼义纲常，"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是和非。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，太师，想我爹爹，将奴送进相府，伏侍太师。我今日梳妆已毕，来到凤仪"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亭游玩散闷。不料那狂厮赶来，调戏于我。正要投池自尽，幸亏太师到来，救"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "了奴的性命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想你爹爹，将你送与吕布为妻，你跟他去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（貂蝉哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我爹爹送奴与太师为妾，我不愿跟随吕布的了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（红衲袄） 勿使啼恨，新郎弃再嫁他人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汝再作恋新弃旧，汝再作恋新弃旧，一旦恩情付与他人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怜我不修礼，是恩情付于流水。"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快随吕布去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太师好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我老了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太师不老。"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那吕布好吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，太师好吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（貂蝉哭。董卓学貂蝉语。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“哎吓，太师吓……”"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢太师。"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下次不可。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们哪里安身才好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我想眉坞郡安然，那里有三十年粮饷，四十万藤甲兵，皇家宫院，城池坚固。"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大事成就，封你为妃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢太师。"
        },
        {
          "character": "董卓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内使们，往眉坞去者。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖尾声〗，貂蝉、董卓同下。）"
        }
      ],
